OL,3,CPolice officer denies stealing cash,
OL,4,Cjewellery and power tool after drugs
OL,5,Cbust
OL,7,FA police officer has pleaded not
OL,8,Fguilty to stealing cash, jewellery and
OL,9,Fa drill from a property following a
OL,10,Fdrugs raid.
OL,12,FPolice constable Robert Davies, 49,
OL,13,Fappeared at Birmingham Crown Court on
OL,14,FWednesday and entered not guilty pleas
OL,15,Fto three counts of theft, all
OL,16,Fconnected to his duties.
