OL,5,Cbust
OL,7,FTwo of the charges allege that the
OL,8,Fofficer, from Alcester, Warwickshire,
OL,9,Fstole cash, jewellery and a power tool
OL,10,Ffrom an address in Redditch,
OL,11,FWorcestershire, in November 2023.
OL,13,FThe third charge alleges that Davies
OL,14,Fstole #180 in cash "belonging to The
OL,15,FCrown" in February last year in
OL,16,FAlcester.
OL,18,FJudge Peter Cooke granted Davies bail
OL,19,Fto reappear for a three-day trial at
OL,20,Fthe same court on May 30 2028.
