OL,7,FAdjourning the case after a seven-
OL,8,Fminute hearing, the judge told Davies:
OL,9,F"You were probably led to expect that
OL,10,Fthe trial was going to be a very long
OL,11,Fway off because of the backlog we are
OL,12,Fsuffering.
OL,14,F"But it is now fixed for May 2028. You
OL,15,Fremain on bail in the meantime."
OL,17,FA previous hearing was told that the
OL,18,Fdefendant was a constable with 21
OL,19,Fyears of service and was alleged to
OL,20,Fhave committed theft while working as
OL,21,Fan exhibits officer.
