OL,13,FConduct (IOPC) announced last year
OL,14,Fthat Davies is accused of three counts
OL,15,Fof theft contrary to sections one and
OL,16,Fseven of the Theft Act 1968.
OL,18,FThe IOPC said in a statement: "The
OL,19,Fcharges relate to the alleged theft of
OL,20,Fcash and property in the course of his
OL,21,Fduties.
